      "text": [
        "4088 - وَ قَالَ : فِي رَجُلٍ اِسْتَأْجَرَ أَجِيراً فَأَقْعَدَهُ عَلَى مَتَاعِهِ فَسُرِقَ قَالَ \"هُوَ مُؤْتَمَنٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4088 - Imam (as) was asked about a man who hired a laborer and entrusted him to guard his goods, but the goods were stolen.\nImam (as) said: \"He is considered trustworthy.\""
        ]
      }
    }
